  1890	
  1891	## Appraisal-note draft and submit APIs (006E)
  1892	
  1893	Protected staff endpoints:
  1894	- `POST /api/v1/loan-applications/{loan_application_id}/appraisal-note/`
  1895	- `GET /api/v1/loan-applications/{loan_application_id}/appraisal-note/`
  1896	- `PATCH /api/v1/loan-applications/{loan_application_id}/appraisal-note/`
  1897	- `POST /api/v1/appraisal-notes/{loan_appraisal_note_id}/submit-for-review/`
  1898	
  1899	Rules:
  1900	- Create requires `credit.appraisal.create`, `credit.risk_assessment.manage`, and the existing
  1901	  application object-access boundary. It requires a stored eligibility projection with
  1902	  `overall_result = eligible` and a stored loan-limit projection; missing or non-eligible facts
  1903	  return `409 INVALID_STATE_TRANSITION` without appraisal, risk, audit, or workflow rows.
  1904	- One appraisal and one linked risk assessment are stored per loan application. The note snapshots
  1905	  the prerequisite assessment UUIDs and user-provided summaries; it never recalculates eligibility,
  1906	  loan limits, policy, or cultivated acreage.
  1907	- Required summaries are non-blank. Recommended amount is positive; optional tenure is a positive
  1908	  integer; supplied interest type is `floating`; recommendation is `approve`, `reject`, or
  1909	  `conditions`; all four risk ratings are `low`, `medium`, or `high`. Unknown top-level or nested
  1910	  fields return `400 VALIDATION_ERROR`.
  1911	- A recommendation above the stored final eligible amount is rejected unless that stored
  1912	  loan-limit projection already has `exception_required_flag = true`; 006E does not create an
  1913	  exception approval.
  1914	- PATCH is draft-only and changes supplied fields only. It requires `credit.appraisal.update`;
  1915	  changing nested risk fields additionally requires `credit.risk_assessment.manage`.
  1916	- GET is side-effect free and is allowed to scoped holders of create/update/submit-review or the
  1917	  Credit Manager review permission. Missing notes return `404 NOT_FOUND`.
  1918	- `tat_due_at` is application `created_at + 2 days` and never resets. At the exact due instant TAT
  1919	  is `within_tat`; later preparation/submission is `breached`.
  1920	- Submit requires `credit.appraisal.submit_review`, object scope, and non-blank `remarks`; it
  1921	  atomically transitions `draft -> review_pending` once. Repeated submit and later PATCH return
  1922	  `409 INVALID_STATE_TRANSITION`.
  1923	- Create/update/submit write `appraisal.created`, `appraisal.updated`, or
  1924	  `appraisal.submitted_for_review` metadata-only audit/workflow evidence. Free-text summaries,
  1925	  mitigation notes, and submit remarks are never copied into evidence JSON.
  1926	
  1927	Response data includes appraisal/application/prerequisite IDs, prepared-user summary/time,
  1928	immutable TAT due/status, all stored appraisal fields, linked risk assessment, recommendation, and
  1929	`appraisal_status = draft|review_pending`.

