## 25.1 HTTP Layer Responsibility

The HTTP layer exposes the platform’s module interfaces to the frontend.

It should be consistent but not leak implementation details.

## 25.2 Standard Response Envelope

```json
{
  "success": true,
  "data": {},
  "meta": {
